document_data.name: Jaseen Drakehorn
document_data.titles: High Blade{{Cite adventurers league/The Sword of Selfaril|8}}
document_data.mainbody: '''Jaseen Drakehorn''' was the [[High Blade]] of [[Mulmaster]].{{Cite adventurers league/The Sword of Selfaril|34}}
document_data.History:
Jaseen quietly ruled Mulmaster, supported by the [[Church of Bane]], until [[1491 DR]]. [[Selfaril Uoumdolphin]], the High Blade who ruled until [[1375 DR]], resurfaced in 1491 DR to challenge her dominion over the city.{{Cite adventurers league/The Sword of Selfaril|8-10}}

Selfaril gained support among the citizens of Mulmaster and challenged Jaseen to a public duel.{{Cite adventurers league/The Sword of Selfaril|19-21}}
document_data.Personality: Jaseen was a devoted follower of [[Bane]].{{Cite adventurers league/The Sword of Selfaril|34}}
